            Playtex Products is one of the leading manufacturers and distributors of personal care and consumer products. Founded in 1932 as the International Latex Corporation, the company sells latex products under the name of Playtex. It offers a variety of skin, feminine and infant care products, including gloves, tampons, infant feeding products and diapers. The company s skin care segment provides Wet Ones brand of hand and face wipes and gloves. Its Banana Boat brand includes a range of sunblock, tanning, sunless tanning and after-sun products. The company s portfolio of infant feeding products includes feeding systems, reusable hard bottles, spill-proof cups and mealtime products. Playtex Products additionally provides child carriers and the Nursing Necessities line of breast care and related products.
          






















